#include <stdio.h>
#include <stdbool.h>
#include "ta_set.h"

void initializeSet(ta_Set* s, int numberOfElemnet){
	s->value = 0;
	s->numberOfElemnet = numberOfElemnet;
}

void addElement(ta_Set* s, int element){
	unsigned long long one = 1;
	s->value |= one<<(element-1);
}

void removeElement(ta_Set* s, int element){
	unsigned long long one = 1;
	s->value ^= one<<(element-1);
}

void printSet(ta_Set s){
	unsigned long long one = 1;
	for(int i=0; i<s.numberOfElemnet; i++){
		if(s.value & one<<i)
			printf("%d ", i+1);
	}
    printf("\n");
}



bool intersect(ta_Set set1, ta_Set set2){
	if(set1.value & set2.value) return true;
	return false;
}
